  card_summary = 'Acceleration posture drill that teaches forward lean, push angle, and split stance from a falling-start entry without full sprint.',
  coach_language = 'Use to teach acceleration lean and push angles before walk-in starts or Output acceleration. Supervision recommended for beginners.',
