  ('a-skip', 'Scale knee height, impact, balance support, and intensity based on symptoms and clearance. Avoid repeated hard accelerations or loss of trunk control unless appropriate.', 'No default male/female dosage split. Scale by training age, sprint experience, mobility, balance, symptoms, and prerequisites.'),
